docs/omar_blog_post.md
docs/roboeval.md
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md
docs/EXTENDING.md
docs/fm_proxy_verification.md
docs/eval_speedup_research.md
docs/gepa_*.md
docs/vla_proxy_design.md
docs/p1_anomaly_report.md
