InternVLA-A1/

# --- Design notes ---
docs/docker_migration_plan.md
docs/action_space_plan.md
docs/liten_adapter_design.md
docs/lerobot_known_issues.md

# --- Other ---
.claude/
images/
requirements/
utils/
backup_data/
bridge_data/
generated_programs/
manual_evaldata/
finetune_data/
